#: qml/Help.qml:25
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Installing Retro Cores"
msgstr "Inštalácia jadier retro"

#: qml/Help.qml:26
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KRetro (non-flatpak) requires you to install emulators, called 'libretro "
"cores'.\n"
"You should find these from your distro's package manager, for example, "
"'libretro-mgba' for the GBA emulator core. Once installed, you can select "
"them in the settings."
msgstr ""
"KRetro (nie flatpak) vyžaduje inštaláciu emulátorov, nazývaných „jadrá "
"libretro“.\n"
"Mali by ste ich nájsť v správcovi balíkov vašej distribúcie, napríklad "
"„libretro-mgba“ pre jadro emulátora GBA. Po inštalácii ich môžete vybrať v "
"nastaveniach."

#: qml/Help.qml:29
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Installing Retro Cores (Flatpak)"
msgstr "Inštalácia jadier retro (Flatpak)"

#: qml/Help.qml:30
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"The flatpak version of KRetro comes with a curated set of cores already. If "
"you installed KRetro from the official flatpak, you are all set!"
msgstr ""
"Verzia KRetro vo flatpaku už obsahuje vybraný súbor jadier. Ak ste "
"nainštalovali KRetro z oficiálneho flatpaku, je všetko pripravené!"

#: qml/Help.qml:35
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Installing Games"
msgstr "Inštalácia hier"

#: qml/Help.qml:39
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@title"
msgid "Adding ROMs"
msgstr "Pridávanie ROMov"

#: qml/Help.qml:40
#, kde-format
msgid ""
"KRetro automatically detects supported games (by file extension) from the "
"ROMs directory (which by default is ~/Documents/Games). Simply add your ROMs "
"there and they will appear in the game library!"
msgstr ""
"KRetro automaticky deteguje podporované hry (podľa prípony súboru) z "
"priečinka ROMov (ktorý je predvolene ~/Documents/Games). Jednoducho tam "
"pridajte svoje ROMy a objavia sa v knižnici hier!"

